metadata.name: Smothered by Death
metadata.description:
1/1 
Ink + Paper 
‪6,833 x 10,346‬  
4800 DPI



a one sided relationship with:  
death  
love  
and pain. 

the death grips of my comfort zone. suffocating me with every breath. i've only known things that were bad for me. it is...my comfort zone. it is all i've ever known... death, love, and pain.
